data.title: Can a good stock investing track record land me a job with a hedge fund without a degree?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): It strikes me as being possible but (very) hard. I think the more difficult question is "How can I get anyone at a hedge fund to take me seriously enough to interview me for a job without a degree?" If you can solve that one the actual getting the job bit is easier I think.
